author: Jeff Johnson
title: Gladwin boys win Northern Michigan Soccer League Championship
text:
Gladwin boys win Northern Michigan Soccer League Championship Posted: 
CLARE - The division champions in the Northern Michigan Soccer League squared off Wednesday night in Clare to determine the Northern Michigan Soccer League title. 
Gladwin stayed unbeaten in conference play with a 4-0 victory against the Bucks. 
McBain Northern Michigan Christian and Burt Lake Northern Michigan Christian played to a 0-0 draw in the Consolation Game. Most Popular Stories Most Popular Stories More>>
